data.actual_result: After minutes of scrolling, you'll see that some results start to get duplicated. The more you scroll, the more the results get duplicated.
data.expected_result: Nothing out of ordinary happens. You just keep going down.
data.short_description: Some search results get duplicated as you scroll down.
data.steps_to_repro: - Search something that gives too many results. - Start scrolling down the search results.
